    {
      "id": "1523236999517962380",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-07-05T08:00:01.06+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": true,
      "content": "\uD83D\uDCE2 Minor update!\n\nIt turns out that the changes to the density rules have not yet been upstreamed to Open PDKs from our legacy wafer.space PDK fork. This update addresses this issue.\n\n- Project Template [1.5.7](https://github.com/wafer-space/gf180mcu-project-template/releases/tag/1.5.7)\n  - Update PDK to `d658698b`\n\n- Precheck [1.7.1](https://github.com/wafer-space/gf180mcu-precheck/releases/tag/1.7.1)\n  - Update PDK to `d658698b`\n\nThe filler generation has already considered these rules. The platform will automatically rerun the latest precheck for your designs.",
      "author": {
        "id": "323371864074485771",
        "name": "mole99",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "Leo Moser (mole99)",
