      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": true,
      "content": "@everyone \uD83D\uDCE2 Critical update!\n\nIf you are using the community-created 3.3V standard cell library for your tapeout, please update your design, as the PDK update fixes a critical issue.\n\n- Project Template [1.5.8](https://github.com/wafer-space/gf180mcu-project-template/releases/tag/1.5.8)\n  - Update PDK to `f6eeac7d`\n    - Fix an issue in `gf180mcu_as_sc_mcu7t3v3` regarding buffer cells.\n\n- Precheck [1.7.2](https://github.com/wafer-space/gf180mcu-precheck/releases/tag/1.7.2)\n  - Fix the text ID generation for narrow letters such as \"I\".\n\nIf there are any questions, please let us know.",
